        <h2>About Dr. Tal Lavian</h2>

        <p>Dr. Tal Lavian is a telecommunications expert specializing in <a href="/communications-expert-witness/data-communications-expert/">data communications</a>, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/computer-networking-expert-witness/">computer networks</a>, and <a href="/communications-expert-witness/internet-expert-witness/">internet protocols (TCP/IP)</a>. With over 35 years of experience as a scientist, educator, and technologist, Dr. Lavian offers expert consulting services in <a href="/communications-expert-witness/network-communications-expert-witness/">telecommunications</a>, network communications, computer communications, and internet protocols. His expertise includes computer networks, data communications, LAN/WAN, TCP/IP, UDP, VPN, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/voice-over-ip-voip-expert/">voice over IP (VoIP)</a>, streaming media, chat, SMS, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/network-communications-expert-witness/">network security</a>, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/mobile-wireless-expert/">mobile wireless</a>, Ethernet, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/routing-switching-expert/">routing</a>, switching, the internet, web technologies, and communication standards.</p>

